text: Nuba most commonly refers to the Nuba peoples. It may also refer to: *Nuba Mountains, the homeland of the Nuba *Nuba languages, the languages of the Nuba Mountains *Nuba fighting, a combat sport of the Nuba *Nuba, Hebron, a Palestinian village *Andalusi nubah, a North African musical form *Nuubaat, an Algerian musical form *Nüba, a deity in Chinese mythology *Nuba (album), an American jazz album
title: Nuba (disambiguation)
